# ubuntu-form-project

This is a simple HTML form project for learning web structure and semantic HTML.

## Contents
- First name and last name
- Date of birth
- Gender
- Opinion on the phrase "Ubuntu"
- Clear, submit, and cancel buttons

## Purpose
This project demonstrates understanding of HTML structure using elements such as:
- header
- nav
- main
- section
- form
- fieldset
- legend
- aside
- footer
